divs: Sighting DetailsWe were jumping on the trampoline when it happened. we noticed it was gettingdarker unusually fast and looked up to see small sheres floating in the sky. Atfirst we thought it was a plane but,it moved too fast and at strange angles.Theyalso hovered...something that a thing that big couldnt do.As we saw it there wasa drop of temperature and we felt we couldnt take our eyes off them until We gota video camer,then we returned to gazing at them. More and more lighsappeared.Some hovered,others went in starnge angles. Others went in straightlines. We lost sight when it flew up into the atmosphere.
